# Atopos Disclosure Policy

## Reporting security issues
If you believe you have discovered a vulnerability in Atopos, please report it responsibly.

### Contact
Email: security@atoposlabs.com

### Include
- A clear description of the issue
- Steps to reproduce
- Impact assessment (if known)
- Any relevant logs or evidence you are comfortable sharing

## Our commitment
We aim to:
- Acknowledge receipt within 72 hours
- Provide a remediation or mitigation plan where appropriate
- Coordinate disclosure timelines in good faith

## Please do not
- Publicly disclose vulnerabilities before we have had a reasonable chance to remediate
- Attempt disruptive testing against production infrastructure without permission
